Package: ggiconZY
Type: Package
Title: Microbiology Figures and Scientific Icons for 'ggplot2'
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: person(
    given = "Yang",
    family = "Zhong",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "yzhong005@users.noreply.github.com",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9146-0875")
  )
Description: Creates reusable microbiology and biological illustrations as
    customizable 'ggplot2' objects. Functions draw scientific icons, bacterial
    streak plates, antimicrobial disc-diffusion assays, and labelled or numeric
    96-well microplates. Common plate-reader exports can be imported from text,
    comma-separated values, or spreadsheet files.
